Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,0:16:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,恶龙 我亲眼看见的{\fs15}\Ndragon. I saw it with me own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他把那个畜生射到了{\fs15}\NHe brought the beast down. shot  him
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,用一把黑箭射死的{\fs15}\Ndead with a Black Arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你救了我们所有人   愿上帝保佑你{\fs15}\NYou've saved us all, bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.64,0:16:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,向恶龙屠杀者致敬{\fs15}\NAll hail to the Dragon-slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,向{\fs15}\NAll hail...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.93,0:16:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,巴德国王致敬{\fs15}\NKing Bard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.71,0:16:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经说过多次 他是一个崇高的人{\fs15}\NI have said it many times, this is a man of noble stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,天生的领袖 - 不要那样叫我{\fs15}\NA born leader. - Do not call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是长湖镇的镇长{\fs15}\NI'm not the Master of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪里{\fs15}\NWhere is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,镇长在哪里  - 在去安都因河的半道上{\fs15}\NWhere's the master? - Half way down the Anduin,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我怀疑  还带着我们的财宝{\fs15}\Nwith all our coin, I don't doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该知道{\fs15}\NYou would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你帮助他把所有财宝{\fs15}\NYou helped him empty the treasury.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没有{\fs15}\N- No,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我试图阻止过你{\fs15}\NI tried to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,骗子 小偷{\fs15}\NLiar! Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.51,0:17:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你个狗杂种 - 求你们 恳求你们了{\fs15}\NYou're a mongrel.- I begged, I pleaded,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过 镇长{\fs15}\NI said: "Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不是{\fs15}\NNo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,为孩子们想想{\fs15}\NThink of the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.06,0:17:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都不为孩子想想吗{\fs15}\NWill nobody think of the children?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 绞死他{\fs15}\NAargh. Hang him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,把他挂在树上{\fs15}\NTo the tree with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,放下他{\fs15}\NLet him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,让他走{\fs15}\NLet him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你们周围{\fs15}\NLook around you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.36,0:18:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你们{\fs15}\NHave you not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,还嫌死得不够多吗{\fs15}\Nhad your fill of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,冬天就要来了{\fs15}\NWinter is upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不仅要照顾自己 还有病人 无家可归的人{\fs15}\NWe must look to our own, to the sick and the helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,还能走动的人 去照料伤者{\fs15}\NThose who can stand, tend to the wounded,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,力气大的人 跟我来{\fs15}\Nand those who have strength left, follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须尽最大努力抢救 - 然后有怎样{\fs15}\NWe must salvage what we can. - And what then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,之后我们做什么{\fs15}\NWhat do we do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找庇护所{\fs15}\NWe find shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.64,0:19:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗{\fs15}\NHello!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,庞博{\fs15}\NBombur?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,波佛{\fs15}\NBifur?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗{\fs15}\NAnybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,等等{\fs15}\NWait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.58,0:19:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这里{\fs15}\NWait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你们必须离开   我们都得离开{\fs15}\NYou need to leave. We all need to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,停 停下{\fs15}\NStop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,停下{\fs15}\NStop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.23,0:19:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你们必须离开 我们都得离开{\fs15}\NYou need to leave. We all need to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们才到这里来呢{\fs15}\NWe only just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟他说过 但他不听劝告{\fs15}\NI tried talking to him, but he won't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你这话什么意思 小伙子 - 是索林{\fs15}\NWho do you mean, laddie? - Thorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.17,0:19:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,索林 索林 他下去有几天了{\fs15}\NThorin. Thorin, he's been down there for days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不休不眠 不吃不喝{\fs15}\NHe doesn't sleep, he barely eats.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他都快变了一个人 这还不算什么 这个地方{\fs15}\NHe's not been himself, not at all. It's this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:20:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这个地方 我觉得会让人得病{\fs15}\Nit's this place. I think a sickness lies upon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.52,0:20:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,会得病{\fs15}\NA sickness?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,得那种病{\fs15}\NWhat kind of sickness?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,菲力{\fs15}\NFíli?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,菲力{\fs15}\NFíli!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.61,0:20:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,菲力{\fs15}\NFíli!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.02,0:20:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,黄金{\fs15}\NGold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.91,0:20:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,多得无法估量{\fs15}\NGold beyond measure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.46,0:20:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,超越痛苦{\fs15}\Nbeyond sorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,超越伤悲{\fs15}\Nand grieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.63,0:21:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,快来看看{\fs15}\NBehold... the great...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,索林祖先留下的宝藏{\fs15}\Ntreasure hoard of Thrór.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎你{\fs15}\NWelcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,侄子{\fs15}\Nmy sisters sons...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,来到孤山{\fs15}\Nto the Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.41,0:21:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,黄金王国{\fs15}\Nof Erebor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.36,0:21:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,巴林{\fs15}\NBalin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.92,0:21:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,波佛{\fs15}\NBofur!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,奇力 毕佛{\fs15}\NKíli! Bifur!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.14,0:21:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,庞博  - 你还活着{\fs15}\NBombur! - You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么发现吗 - 没有{\fs15}\NAny sign of it? - Nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有  - 继续找{\fs15}\NNothing here. - Keep searching!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.63,0:21:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,珠宝可能会在任何地方{\fs15}\NThat jewel could be any where
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.30,0:21:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,阿肯宝钻肯定还在这里面{\fs15}\NThe Arkenstone is in these halls.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,找到它 - 你听到了 快找{\fs15}\NFind it! - You heard him, keep looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.31,0:21:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,都去找{\fs15}\NAll of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.51,0:21:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,直到找到{\fs15}\NNo-one rests until it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,为止{\fs15}\Nfound!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.63,0:22:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,差点就诱导你找到钻石了{\fs15}\NI am almost tempted to let you take it,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.01,0:22:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想{\fs15}\Nif only...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.68,0:22:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,看到索林・橡木盾{\fs15}\Nto see Oakenshield..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.70,0:22:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,经受折磨{\fs15}\Nsuffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.32,0:22:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,看着钻石{\fs15}\NWatch it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.37,0:22:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,摧毁他{\fs15}\Ndestroy him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,看着钻石腐蚀{\fs15}\NWatch it corrupt...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他的心{\fs15}\Nhis heart...{\fs15}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.20,0:22:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,让他疯掉{\fs15}\Nand drive him mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.03,0:23:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,带着你所需要的{\fs15}\NTake only what you need,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.32,0:23:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还有很远的路要走 - 我们要走哪里去{\fs15}\Nwe have a long march ahead. - Where will you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.41,0:23:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一个地方可去{\fs15}\NThere is only one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.87,0:23:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,孤山{\fs15}\NThe Mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.84,0:23:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你可真聪明 镇长{\fs15}\NYou are a genius, Sire.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.53,0:23:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以在山里避难{\fs15}\NWe can take refuge inside the Mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.50,0:23:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有恶龙的气味 女人们可以打扫干净{\fs15}\NIt might smell a bit of dragon. The women could clean it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.08,0:23:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那里将会很安全 暖和 干燥 储存丰富{\fs15}\NIt will be safe and warm and dry, and full of stores,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.33,0:23:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有床和衣物{\fs15}\Nbedding and clothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.84,0:23:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你的黄金{\fs15}\Nyour bit of gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.39,0:24:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,山上的黄金 是被诅咒了的{\fs15}\NWhat gold is in that Mountain, is cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.42,0:24:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只取应得的那一份{\fs15}\NWe will take only what was promised to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.81,0:24:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,用来我们重建家园{\fs15}\Nonly what we need to rebuild...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.51,0:24:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,和维持生活{\fs15}\Nour lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.86,0:24:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,来 再加点重量{\fs15}\NHere, pull your weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.35,0:24:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,史矛革被屠杀的消息会传遍整个大陆{\fs15}\NNews of the death of Smaug will have spread through the lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.84,0:24:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是{\fs15}\NAye.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.27,0:24:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有的人就会觊觎{\fs15}\NOthers will now look to the Mountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.62,0:24:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,山上的财富{\fs15}\Nfor it's wealth...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.23,0:24:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,或者位置在哪里 - 你还知道什么{\fs15}\Nor it's position. - What is it you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.71,0:24:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,都不好说 只是担心会发生而已{\fs15}\NNothing for certain. It's what I fear may come.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.39,0:24:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,精灵之王
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.31,0:24:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}精灵国王的儿子和一个女精灵{\fs15}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.27,0:24:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,把我们困在了长湖镇{\fs15}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.23,0:25:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那你把他们都杀了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.91,0:25:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他们像胆小鬼一样
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.12,0:25:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,尖叫着逃跑了{\fs15}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.29,0:25:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,蠢货 他们还会回来的{\fs15}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.16,0:25:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,到时候会带着精灵大军
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.59,0:25:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,到冈达巴山{\fs15}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.09,0:25:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,让军队出发
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.89,0:25:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.98,0:25:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,人族
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.35,0:25:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,矮人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.40,0:25:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,孤山会是他们的葬生之地
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.90,0:25:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,开战
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.36,0:25:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你在那边看见什么了{\fs15}\NYou saw something out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.06,0:25:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,追到长湖镇的半兽人军团 我知道是谁了{\fs15}\NThe Orc I pursued out of Lake-town, I know who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.29,0:25:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,博尔格 阿索格产的卵{\fs15}\NBolg, the spawn of Azog the Defiler.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.76,0:25:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他知道我们在伊瑞德米斯林等着他{\fs15}\NA Wargpack was waiting for him on the outskirts of Esgorath.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.96,0:25:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,便逃往北方去了{\fs15}\NThey fled into the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.76,0:25:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这些半兽人和其他以前的不一样{\fs15}\NThese Orcs were different from the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.45,0:26:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有一个标志 我已经很久没有看到过了{\fs15}\Nthey bore a mark I had not seen for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.34,0:26:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,刚达巴山的标记{\fs15}\NThe mark of Gundabad.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.16,0:26:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,冈达巴山{\fs15}\NGundabad?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.50,0:26:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,远离迷雾山脉北方的一个半兽人大本营{\fs15}\NAn Orc stronghold in the far north of the Misty Mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.26,0:26:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,尊贵的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.68,0:26:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲让我给你带句话
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.98,0:26:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,让你立即返回
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.10,0:26:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,走 塔瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.40,0:26:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.02,0:26:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,她已经被放逐了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.15,0:26:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,放逐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.82,0:26:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你回去告诉我父亲{\fs15}\NYou may tell my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.86,0:26:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没有塔瑞尔 我哪儿也不去{\fs15}\Nif there is no place for Tauriel, there is no place for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.33,0:26:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,莱戈拉斯{\fs15}\NLegolas,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.70,0:26:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你国王的命令{\fs15}\Nit is your King's command.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.79,0:26:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 他是我的国王
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.04,0:26:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但他命令改变不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.27,0:26:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我要到北边去 你要和我一起来吗{\fs15}\NI ride north. Will you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.83,0:26:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,到哪里去    - 冈达巴山{\fs15}\NTo where? - To Gundabad.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.64,0:27:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,咒语是救不了你的 老头
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.59,0:28:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.88,0:28:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,去死吧 老巫师
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.28,0:28:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,天空之下有精灵三戒
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.58,0:28:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,石头大厅里有矮人王国
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.48,0:28:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,凡人注定会死{\fs15}\NNine for mortal men doomed to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.24,0:29:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你无法战胜幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.40,0:29:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,更何况你很虚弱
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.87,0:29:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.00,0:29:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,独自一人在黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.51,0:29:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有同伴{\fs15}\NI am not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.35,0:29:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人 你需要什么帮助吗{\fs15}\NAre you in need of assistance, My Lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.42,0:29:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你们应该留在那里{\fs15}\NYou should have stayed...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.31,0:29:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,等死{\fs15}\Ndead!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.90,0:30:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,米斯兰迪尔{\fs15}\NMithrandir...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.54,0:30:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒{\fs15}\Ncome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.75,0:30:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他 他在这里{\fs15}\NH- He is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.25,0:30:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 黑暗已经来临{\fs15}\NHe is. The darkness has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.46,0:30:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,甘道夫{\fs15}\NGandalf!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.33,0:30:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,甘道夫{\fs15}\NGandalf,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.32,0:30:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,快爬上来{\fs15}\Nclimb on!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.45,0:30:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他太虚弱{\fs15}\NHe is weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.58,0:31:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不能呆在这里了  这是在消耗他的生命{\fs15}\NHe cannot remain here, it is straining his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.53,0:31:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,走{\fs15}\NGo,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.78,0:31:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,快点{\fs15}\Nquickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.62,0:31:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,和我一起走{\fs15}\NCome with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.09,0:31:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人{\fs15}\NMy... Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.50,0:31:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,快走{\fs15}\NGo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.70,0:31:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,都开始了{\fs15}\Nit has begin
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.36,0:32:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,东方将会陨落
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.20,0:32:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,安格玛王国将会崛起{\fs15}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.41,0:32:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,精灵的时代已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.84,0:32:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,半兽人的时代来临
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.80,0:32:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这里{\fs15}\NYou have no...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.42,0:32:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,没有能量{\fs15}\Npower here,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.90,0:32:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,魔多之仆{\fs15}\Nservant of Mordor.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.40,0:32:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你{\fs15}\NYou...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.46,0:32:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不会成形{\fs15}\Nare nameless,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.49,0:32:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,没有面部{\fs15}\Nfaceless,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.17,0:32:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,没有形体{\fs15}\Nformless!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.38,0:32:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,快回到你的虚无世界{\fs15}\NGo back to the void...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.12,0:32:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你本该待的地方{\fs15}\Nfrom whence you came!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.40,0:33:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.99,0:33:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,魔王索伦已被驱逐{\fs15}\NThe spirit of Sauron endured...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.38,0:33:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他的精神受损{\fs15}\Nand has been banished.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.37,0:33:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,将会逃到东方去{\fs15}\NHe will flee into the East.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.76,0:33:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,必须给刚铎警告{\fs15}\NGondor should be warned.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.00,0:33:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他们肯定在监视着魔多的动静{\fs15}\NThey must set a watch on the walls of Mordor.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.71,0:33:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不 照顾好凯兰崔尔夫人{\fs15}\NNo. Look after the Lady Galadriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.39,0:33:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,她肯定耗费了太多的能量 快撑不住了{\fs15}\NShe has spent much of her powers, her strength is failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.57,0:33:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,带她到罗斯洛立安城{\fs15}\NTake her to Lothlórien.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.11,0:33:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,萨鲁曼大人{\fs15}\NMy Lord Saruman,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.75,0:33:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一定要乘胜追击{\fs15}\Nhe must be hunted down...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.66,0:33:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,摧毁他     一劳永逸{\fs15}\Nand destroyed, once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.95,0:33:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没有魔戒的能量{\fs15}\NWithout the Ring of Power,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.29,0:33:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,魔王索伦永远不会再次掌控中土世界{\fs15}\NSauron can never again hold dominion over Middle Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.63,0:33:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走{\fs15}\NGo now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.62,0:34:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不管索伦{\fs15}\NLeave Sauron to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.81,0:34:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要一匹马 - 什么{\fs15}\NI need a horse. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.06,0:34:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,甘道夫{\fs15}\NGandalf,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.12,0:34:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你要到哪里去 - 警告孤王埃雷博{\fs15}\Nwhere are you going? - To warn Erebor.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.26,0:34:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不清楚将要到来的事  我亲眼{\fs15}\NThey have no idea what is coming. I saw them...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.87,0:34:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,看见过他们{\fs15}\Nwith my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.03,0:34:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一排排的莫瑞亚半兽人{\fs15}\NRank upon rank of Moria Orcs.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.41,0:34:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你得告诉我们的朋友 鸟类 野兽{\fs15}\NYou must summon our friends, bird and beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.49,0:34:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,孤山一战就要来了{\fs15}\NThe battle for the Mountain is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.71,0:34:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,它们就在这些大厅里{\fs15}\NIt is here in these halls,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.99,0:34:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 - 我们必须反复寻找{\fs15}\NI know it. - We have searched and searched.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.32,0:34:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,直到找到为止 - 索林{\fs15}\NNot well enough. - Thorin,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.50,0:34:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都看到宝石回到这里来的{\fs15}\Nwe all would see the stone returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.34,0:34:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在还没有找到{\fs15}\N- And yet it's still not found!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.16,0:34:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怀疑我们的忠诚 在场的所有人{\fs15}\NDo you doubt the loyalty of anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.75,0:35:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,阿肯宝钻是族人的神圣之物{\fs15}\NThe Arkenstone is the birthright of our people.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.21,0:35:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是国王的象征{\fs15}\NIt is the King's jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.38,0:35:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,难道我不是王吗{\fs15}\NAm I not the King?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.33,0:35:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,记清楚{\fs15}\NKnow this,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.57,0:35:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有谁找到{\fs15}\Nif anyone should find it...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.47,0:35:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,却不给我{\fs15}\Nand withhold it from me...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.18,0:35:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让他付出代价{\fs15}\NI will be avenged.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.69,0:35:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,恶龙的呕吐物{\fs15}\NDragon sickness...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.87,0:35:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前见过{\fs15}\NI've seen it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.35,0:35:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,听着{\fs15}\NThat look,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.06,0:36:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,有人拿着这个{\fs15}\Nthe terrible need.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.36,0:36:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那是何等残暴而又恐惧的爱  比尔博{\fs15}\NIt is a fierce and jealous love, Bilbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.74,0:36:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,把他的祖父逼疯了{\fs15}\NIt sent his grandfather mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.98,0:36:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,巴林 如果索林{\fs15}\NBalin, if-if Thorin...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.98,0:36:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,得到了阿肯宝钻{\fs15}\Nhad the Arkenstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.70,0:36:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 如果找到了{\fs15}\NWell, if-if it was found...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.54,0:36:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,会对他有帮助吗{\fs15}\Nwould it help?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.49,0:36:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那个宝石{\fs15}\NThat stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.58,0:36:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,代表一切{\fs15}\Ncrowns all.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.48,0:36:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是这里最值钱的宝物{\fs15}\NIt's the summit of this great wealth,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.52,0:36:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,代表无上权力{\fs15}\Nbestowing power...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.73,0:36:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是他所不能承受的{\fs15}\Nupon he who bears it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.90,0:36:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那他会疯掉吗{\fs15}\NBut stay his madness?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.67,0:36:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不 小子{\fs15}\NNo, lad...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.10,0:36:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得比疯了还可怕{\fs15}\NI fear it would make him worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.67,0:36:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,也许这个东西{\fs15}\NPerhaps it is best...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.44,0:36:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,找不到更好{\fs15}\Nit remains lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.93,0:37:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么{\fs15}\NWhat is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.59,0:37:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你手里的那个{\fs15}\NIn your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.34,0:37:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没 没什么 - 给我看看{\fs15}\NIt-it's nothing. - Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.91,0:37:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是{\fs15}\NIt
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.34,0:37:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我从比翁的花园里捡的{\fs15}\NI picked it up in Beorn's garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.67,0:37:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你就一路带着{\fs15}\NYou've carried it all this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.46,0:37:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我打算回去 种在袋底洞的花园里{\fs15}\NI'm going to plant it in my garden. In Bag-End.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.91,0:37:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这也算是带回夏尔的一点点礼物{\fs15}\NThat's a poor prize to take back to the Shire.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.98,0:37:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天它会长大{\fs15}\NOne day it will grow...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.06,0:37:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,每当我看到它 就会想起{\fs15}\Nand every time I look at it, I'll remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.67,0:37:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,想起所有发生过的事 好的 不好的{\fs15}\Nremember everything that happened, the good, the bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.44,0:37:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我是如何辛苦的把它带回家{\fs15}\Nand how lucky I am that I made it home.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.80,0:38:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,索林 我 索林{\fs15}\NThorin, I... Thorin,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.96,0:38:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,长湖镇的幸存者 都往河谷镇避难去了{\fs15}\Nthe survivors from Lake-town, they're streaming into Dale.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.89,0:38:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,数以百计的难民{\fs15}\NThere's hundreds of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.46,0:38:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,叫所有人到门口来{\fs15}\NCall everyone to the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.72,0:38:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,到门口 现在{\fs15}\NTo the gate. Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.11,0:38:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,快点{\fs15}\NCome on,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.45,0:38:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,继续走 - 镇长{\fs15}\Nkeep moving. - Sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.99,0:39:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,镇长{\fs15}\NSire!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.89,0:39:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,快上来{\fs15}\NUp here!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.20,0:39:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,快看镇长 火盆还亮着{\fs15}\NLook Sire! The braziers are lit.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.71,0:39:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,所以{\fs15}\NSo,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.72,0:39:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,索林他们还活着{\fs15}\Nthe company of Thorin Oakenshield survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.18,0:39:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,还活着{\fs15}\NSurvived?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.40,0:39:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说那一群矮人和满屋的黄金在一起{\fs15}\NYou mean there's a bunch of Dwarves in there with all that gold?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.03,0:39:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你不必担心 艾福德{\fs15}\NYou shouldn't worry, Alfrid.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.30,0:39:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,孤山上的黄金多得你无法想象{\fs15}\NThere's gold enough in that Mountain for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.11,0:39:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚在这里过夜{\fs15}\NMake camp here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.39,0:39:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,自己去找留宿的地方{\fs15}\NFind what shelter you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.40,0:39:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,升几堆火起来{\fs15}\NGet some fires going.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.24,0:39:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 快去 - 艾福德{\fs15}\NCome on, hurry along now. - Alfrid,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.64,0:39:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你今晚守夜{\fs15}\Nyou take the night watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.34,0:39:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,推{\fs15}\NPush!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.57,0:40:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我要堡垒在天亮之前堆好{\fs15}\NI want this Fortress made safe by sun-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.92,0:40:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,得到孤山并不容易{\fs15}\NThis Mountain was hard-won,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.31,0:40:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让它再次被夺走{\fs15}\NI will not see it taken again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.46,0:40:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,长湖镇的难民一无所有{\fs15}\NThe people of Lake-town have nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.83,0:40:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在困境中向我们求助{\fs15}\NThey came to us in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.46,0:40:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他们失去了一切{\fs15}\NThey have lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.22,0:40:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不要告诉我他们失去了什么{\fs15}\NDo not tell me what they have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.53,0:40:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我理解他们的艰难{\fs15}\NI know well enough their hardship.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.27,0:40:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那些在恶龙之火中活下来的人{\fs15}\NThose who've lived through dragon fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.50,0:40:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,应该值得庆幸  他们应该{\fs15}\Nshould rejoice! They have...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.97,0:40:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,心存感激{\fs15}\Nmuch to be grateful for.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.95,0:40:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,多弄点石头{\fs15}\NMore stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.12,0:40:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,门口的石头再多点{\fs15}\NBring more stone to the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.57,0:41:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们正挨着饿 我们需要食物{\fs15}\NThese children are starving. We need food.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.67,0:41:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们坚持不了三天了{\fs15}\NWe won't last three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.85,0:41:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,巴德 我们也没有多的 - 尽你所能  珀西{\fs15}\NBard, we don't have enough. - Do what you can, Percy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.96,0:41:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的 不要担心 - 我们需要更多的水{\fs15}\NIt will be all right, don't worry. - We need more water.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.38,0:41:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,先给孩子 受伤的人 女人喝水{\fs15}\NThe children and the wounded and the women come first.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.88,0:41:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 艾福德{\fs15}\NMorning, Alfrid,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.07,0:41:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,夜里有没有什么动静{\fs15}\Nwhat news from the night watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.65,0:41:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,很安静 镇长 没什么可汇报的{\fs15}\NAll quiet, Sire. Not much to report.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.72,0:41:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么经过我们{\fs15}\NNothing gets past me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.70,0:41:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,除了一队精灵族的军队 看起来是这样{\fs15}\NExcept an army of Elves, it would seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.89,0:42:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,瑟兰迪尔大人  请恕我们没有{\fs15}\NMy Lord Thranduil, we did not...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.39,0:42:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,看见你在这里 - 听说你需要帮助{\fs15}\Nlook to see you here. - I heard you needed aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.39,0:42:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你救了我们{\fs15}\NYou have saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.59,0:42:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道怎么报答你{\fs15}\NI do not know how to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.84,0:42:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 收起你的感谢{\fs15}\N- Your gratitude is misplaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.91,0:42:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是专为救你而来{\fs15}\NI did not come on your behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.67,0:42:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我是来取回属于我的东西{\fs15}\NI came to reclaim something of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.71,0:43:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,孤山上的珠宝也是我想得到的东西{\fs15}\NThere are gems in the Mountain that I too desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.16,0:43:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,白色的发着纯光的珠宝{\fs15}\NWhite gems of pure starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.95,0:43:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,绿叶森林的白色珠宝{\fs15}\NThe White gems of Lasgalen.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.25,0:43:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我想精灵王一定会为这些开出很高的价格{\fs15}\NI know an Elf-lord who will pay a pretty price for these.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.04,0:43:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,等等{\fs15}\NWait!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.95,0:43:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,请 等一下{\fs15}\NPlease, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.17,0:43:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为一点财宝你就要去打仗{\fs15}\NYou will go to war over a handful of gems?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.87,0:43:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,族人的家传之宝是 不会被轻易的遗弃{\fs15}\NThe heirlooms of my people are not lightly forsaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.69,0:43:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这点我们在同一战线上{\fs15}\NWe are allies in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.60,0:43:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我的族人{\fs15}\NMy people...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.70,0:43:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,也需要对山上的财宝讨个说法{\fs15}\Nalso have claim upon the riches in that Mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.98,0:43:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,让我去和索林说{\fs15}\NLet me speak with Thorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.89,0:43:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是不想和矮人打交道吗{\fs15}\NYou would try to reason with the Dwarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.40,0:43:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,为了避免冲突{\fs15}\NTo avoid war?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.91,0:43:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是的{\fs15}\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.88,0:43:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,做的好 不错{\fs15}\NNice going lads, nice work.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.62,0:43:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,过来{\fs15}\NCome on!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.67,0:44:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,尊贵的索林 索恩之子{\fs15}\NHail Thorin, son of Thráin.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.43,0:44:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,很高心在绝望之中 得知你们还活着{\fs15}\NWe are glad to find you alive beyond hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.01,0:44:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你为何不去山下的关口{\fs15}\NWhy do you come to gates of the King
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.75,0:44:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,带领军队打仗{\fs15}\Nunder the Mountain armed for war?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.45,0:44:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那为何孤山之王也把他自己围住{\fs15}\NWhy does the King under the Mountain fence himself in...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.57,0:44:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,像强盗一般缩在洞里{\fs15}\Nlike a robber in his hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.59,0:44:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是因为我不想遭到抢劫而已{\fs15}\NPerhaps it is because I'm expecting to be robbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.41,0:44:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,大王{\fs15}\NMy Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.45,0:44:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来这里不是抢劫  是来讨一个公正的说法{\fs15}\Nwe have not come to rob you, but to seek fair settlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.83,0:44:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想下来和我说吗{\fs15}\NWill you not speak with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.30,0:45:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,洗耳恭听{\fs15}\NI'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.78,0:45:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我仅代表长湖镇的人们问你  你要信守你的承诺{\fs15}\NOn behalf of Te people of Lake-town, I ask that you honour your pledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.94,0:45:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,只需要分出一点财物{\fs15}\NA share of the treasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.86,0:45:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们能够重新正常生活{\fs15}\Nso that they might rebuild their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.04,0:45:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会对任何人那样{\fs15}\NI will not treat with any man,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.98,0:45:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,更何况一个他正拿着武器站在我的门口{\fs15}\Nwhile an armed host lies before my door.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.32,0:45:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我想如果协议没有达成 他也会袭击这座山{\fs15}\NThat armed host will attack this mountain if we do not come to terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.55,0:45:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,威胁也吓不到我{\fs15}\NAnd your threats do not sway me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.12,0:45:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你良心何在{\fs15}\NWhat of your conscience?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.60,0:45:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道我们都是拜你所赐{\fs15}\NDoes it not tell you our cause is just?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.17,0:46:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我的人民帮助过你{\fs15}\NMy people offered you help...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.66,0:46:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,而你带给他们只有死亡和毁灭{\fs15}\Nand in return you brought upon them only ruin and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.48,0:46:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,当长湖镇的人来寻求我们帮助的时候{\fs15}\NWhen did the men of Lake-town come to our aid
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.46,0:46:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说过会有丰厚的报酬{\fs15}\Nbut for the promise of rich reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.97,0:46:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,报酬还不多吗{\fs15}\NA bargain was struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.51,0:46:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,什么报酬{\fs15}\NA bargain?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.10,0:46:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也只有用继承的财物{\fs15}\NWhat choice did we have but to barter
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.06,0:46:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,廉价换得毯子{\fs15}\Nour birthright for blankets...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.08,0:46:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,食物  那是在用我们的{\fs15}\Nand food. To ransom our...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.15,0:46:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,未来换得自由 你还说那是公平的交易吗{\fs15}\Nfuture in exchange for our freedom. You call that a fair trade?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.86,0:46:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我 恶龙屠杀者巴德{\fs15}\NTell me, Bard the dragon-slayer,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.26,0:46:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我该如何信守承诺{\fs15}\Nwhy should I honour such terms?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.32,0:46:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你给了我们{\fs15}\NBecause you gave us your...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.36,0:46:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,承诺{\fs15}\Nword.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.36,0:46:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,难道那也是假的{\fs15}\NDoes that mean nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.23,0:47:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,快走吧 在我还没放箭{\fs15}\NBegone, ere our arrows...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.28,0:47:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,之前{\fs15}\Nfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.39,0:47:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么{\fs15}\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.40,0:47:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能挑起一场战争{\fs15}\NYou cannot go to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.24,0:47:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这和你没关系 - 你说什么{\fs15}\NThis does not concern you. - Excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.62,0:47:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你没注意到{\fs15}\Nbut just in case you haven't noticed,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.01,0:47:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,外面有一只精灵大军吗{\fs15}\Nthere is an army of Elves out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.37,0:47:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,更别说有几百个愤怒的渔民{\fs15}\NNot to mention several hundred angry fishermen.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.01,0:47:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我们寡不敌众啊{\fs15}\NW-w-we are in fact outnumbered.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.34,0:47:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不会太久的{\fs15}\NNot for much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.35,0:47:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么意思{\fs15}\NWhat does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.41,0:47:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是  聪明的巴金斯{\fs15}\NIt means, Master Baggins,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.10,0:47:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你真不该低估矮人{\fs15}\Nyou should never underestimate Dwarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.19,0:47:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,以前我们抵抗埃雷博{\fs15}\NWe have reclaimed Erebor.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.16,0:48:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们反抗{\fs15}\NNow we defend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.83,0:48:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他什么都不会给我们{\fs15}\NHe will give us nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.43,0:48:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真遗憾 至少{\fs15}\NSuch a pity. But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.43,0:48:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你试过了  - 我只是不明白{\fs15}\Nyou tried. - I do not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.41,0:48:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么{\fs15}\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.49,0:48:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么他要冒着打仗的风险{\fs15}\NWhy would he risk war?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.08,0:48:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,和他们谈判就是徒劳 他们只明白了{\fs15}\NIt is fruitless to reason with them. They understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.69,0:48:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一件事{\fs15}\Nonly one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.42,0:48:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在拂晓发起攻击{\fs15}\NWe attack at dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.78,0:49:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你要一起吗{\fs15}\NAre you with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.82,0:49:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,巴金斯学士 过来{\fs15}\NMaster Baggins, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.22,0:50:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你会需要这个的{\fs15}\NYou're going to need this.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.92,0:50:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,穿上它{\fs15}\NPut it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.36,0:50:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这件背心由银质金属做成{\fs15}\NThis vest is made of silver steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.23,0:50:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我的祖先叫它秘银背心{\fs15}\NMithril it was called by my forebears.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.84,0:50:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,刀剑不入{\fs15}\NNo blade can pierce it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.53,0:50:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,很好笑吧 我不是战士 只是一个矮人{\fs15}\NI look absurd. I'm not a warrior, I'm a Hobbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.86,0:50:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这是礼物{\fs15}\NIt is a gift,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.91,0:50:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们友谊的象征{\fs15}\Na token of our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.90,0:50:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真心朋友从来都是难遇{\fs15}\NTrue friends are hard to come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.35,0:50:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前看走了眼 不过现在能看清一些事了{\fs15}\NI have been blind, but now I'm beginning to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.88,0:50:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我被背叛了{\fs15}\NI am betrayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.86,0:50:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,叛徒{\fs15}\NBetrayed?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.54,0:51:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那个阿肯宝钻{\fs15}\NThe Arkenstone...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.87,0:51:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他们中有人拿去了{\fs15}\None of them has taken it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.94,0:51:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定有一人撒谎{\fs15}\NOne of them is false.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.52,0:51:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,索林{\fs15}\NThorin,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.00,0:51:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,探索完成 你也赢得了孤山{\fs15}\Nthe quest is fulfilled, you've won the Mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.94,0:51:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那还不够吗{\fs15}\NIs that not enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.81,0:51:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,被同族背叛 - 不 额{\fs15}\NBetrayed by my own kin. - No, eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.16,0:51:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你       - 你对长湖镇的人们许过承诺{\fs15}\Nyou - you made a promise to the people of Lake-town.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.90,0:51:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,难道是{\fs15}\NIs this...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.95,0:51:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,财宝比你自己的荣耀更值钱吗{\fs15}\Ntreasure truly worth more than your honour?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.78,0:51:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的荣耀 索林 我当时也在那里 我许下了诺言{\fs15}\NOur honour, Thorin. I was also there, I gave my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.43,0:51:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 正因如此  我心怀感激{\fs15}\N- For that, I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.24,0:51:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那是崇高的人做的事 但是孤山{\fs15}\NThat was nobly done. But the treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.01,0:51:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,的财宝的确不是属于{\fs15}\Nin this Mountain does not belong to the...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.92,0:51:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,长湖镇的人{\fs15}\Npeople of Lake-town.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.42,0:51:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这些黄金{\fs15}\NThis gold...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.77,0:51:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是我们的{\fs15}\Nis ours...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.18,0:52:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,也只能是我们的{\fs15}\Nand ours alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.22,0:52:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,用我的生命起誓{\fs15}\NWith my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.12,0:52:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会把一分钱{\fs15}\NI will not part...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.39,0:52:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,分出去{\fs15}\Nwith a single coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.45,0:52:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,一点儿{\fs15}\NNot...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.06,0:52:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,也不会{\fs15}\None piece of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.82,0:52:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,冈达巴山{\fs15}\NGundabad.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.39,0:52:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那边是什么 - 我们的宿敌{\fs15}\NWhat lies beyond? - An old enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.65,0:52:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,古老的{\fs15}\NThe ancient Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.63,0:52:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,安格玛王国{\fs15}\Nof Angmar.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.38,0:53:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这些堡垒曾经是他们的大本营{\fs15}\NThis fortress was once it's stronghold.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.00,0:53:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是他们补给装备{\fs15}\NIt is where they kept their great armouries,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.15,0:53:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,打造兵器的兵工厂{\fs15}\Nforged their weapons of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.28,0:53:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,光 有动静{\fs15}\NA light. I saw movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.22,0:53:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们等到夜色来临{\fs15}\NWe wait for the cover of night.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.89,0:53:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这个地方很凶险 塔瑞尔{\fs15}\NIt is a fell place, Tauriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.55,0:53:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很早的年代 我们的祖先向这片土地{\fs15}\NIn another age our people waged war on...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.06,0:53:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,开战{\fs15}\Nthose lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.82,0:53:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我的母亲死于此{\fs15}\NMy mother died there.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.28,0:53:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲从不提起这件事{\fs15}\NMy father does not speak of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.33,0:53:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这里没有坟墓{\fs15}\NThere is no grave,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.19,0:53:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没有碑石{\fs15}\Nno memory,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.32,0:53:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有{\fs15}\Nnothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.43,0:53:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,让我过去{\fs15}\NLet me through!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.09,0:54:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,让开{\fs15}\NMake way!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.71,0:54:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不{\fs15}\NNo, no,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.90,0:54:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不 诶 你{\fs15}\Nno! Oi, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.49,0:54:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,尖帽子那个{\fs15}\NPointy hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.47,0:54:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,对{\fs15}\NYes...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.34,0:54:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你{\fs15}\Nyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.48,0:54:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不收流浪汉 乞丐{\fs15}\NWe don't want no tramps, beggars...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.61,0:54:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这里不需要流浪汉{\fs15}\Nnor vagabonds around here
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.15,0:54:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,即使没有你这种人 我们的麻烦都够多了{\fs15}\NWe've got enough trouble without the likes of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.74,0:54:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以走了{\fs15}\NOff you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.66,0:54:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,骑上你的马{\fs15}\NOn your horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.49,0:54:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这里谁说了算{\fs15}\NWho's in charge here?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.45,0:54:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁在问{\fs15}\NWho is asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.37,0:54:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,必须把你和矮人的小事放在一边{\fs15}\NYou must set aside your petty grievances with the dwarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.53,0:54:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,战争就要来了{\fs15}\NWar is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.51,0:54:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,多尔戈多已经有大批敌人驻扎{\fs15}\NThe cesspits of Dol Guldur have been emptied.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.09,0:54:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你们正处于危险之中{\fs15}\NYou're all in mortal danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.89,0:54:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么{\fs15}\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.41,0:54:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你对巫师一无所知{\fs15}\NI can see you know nothing of wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.28,0:55:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是冬日旷野里的一声雷响  滚滚的来自远方{\fs15}\NThey are like winter thunder on a wild wind, rolling in from a distance...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.92,0:55:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,故作姿态 让人惊慌{\fs15}\Nbreaking hard and alarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.98,0:55:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但有时风暴{\fs15}\NBut sometimes a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.31,0:55:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,仅仅只是风暴{\fs15}\Nis just a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.18,0:55:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这次不同{\fs15}\NNot this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.94,0:55:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,半兽人军队正在行军{\fs15}\NArmies of Orcs are on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.63,0:55:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那些都是战士 为战争而生{\fs15}\NThese are fighters, they have been bred for war.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.20,0:55:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人们都鼓起了全部士气{\fs15}\NOur enemy has summoned his full strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.11,0:55:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么现在才有此目的 - 因为{\fs15}\NWhy show his hand now? - Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.91,0:55:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,被我们逼的{\fs15}\Nwe forced him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.66,0:55:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,当索林一行人出发去他们家园征讨的时候{\fs15}\NWe forced him when the company of Thorin Oakenshield
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.72,0:55:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就逼上绝路了{\fs15}\Nset out to reclaim their homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.43,0:55:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,矮人从来都不曾真的想到孤山{\fs15}\NThe Dwarves were never meant to reach Erebor,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.06,0:55:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是安玛格奉命前去追杀他们{\fs15}\NAzog the Defiler was sent to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.06,0:55:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他们首领想要控制住孤山{\fs15}\NHis master seeks control of the Mountain,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.39,0:55:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅仅是因为那里面有财宝{\fs15}\Nnot just for the treasure within,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.27,0:55:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,而是孤山的位置 很具有战略性{\fs15}\Nbut for where it lies, it's strategic position.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.53,0:55:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是北方{\fs15}\NThis is the gateway to...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.73,0:55:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,征讨安格玛军队的要塞{\fs15}\Nreclaiming the lands of Angmar in the North.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.11,0:55:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这个罪恶的王国崛起{\fs15}\NIf that fell Kingdom should rise again...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.53,0:55:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞文戴尔  罗瑞安 夏尔{\fs15}\NRivendell, Lórien, the Shire...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.79,0:55:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至刚铎王国也会被侵占{\fs15}\Neven Gondor itself will  fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.61,0:56:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的这些半兽人军队 米斯兰迪尔{\fs15}\NThese Orc armies you speak of, Mithrandir,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.57,0:56:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他们现在在哪里{\fs15}\Nwhere are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.65,0:56:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,军队将会在黎明前就位
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.32,0:56:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,给他们来一个突然袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.03,0:56:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那些蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.07,0:56:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,早就忘记这片大地上的生灵
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.54,0:56:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,忘记了伟大的大陆统治者
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.14,0:56:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们要进去 - 现在就行动
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.32,0:56:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,它们在聚集
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.46,0:57:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这些蝙蝠繁殖只有一个目的{\fs15}\NThese bats are bred for one purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.76,0:57:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什么目的{\fs15}\NFor what?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.55,0:57:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,为了战争{\fs15}\NFor war.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.04,0:57:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,必须警告其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.58,0:57:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,也许晚了 - 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.54,0:58:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候我们变得如此重要了{\fs15}\NSince when has my council counted for so little?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.90,0:58:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为我一直在做什么{\fs15}\NWhat do you think I'm trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.74,0:58:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你一直都只是在救你的矮人朋友{\fs15}\NI think you're trying to save your Dwarvish friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.61,0:58:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该赞美你对他们的忠诚{\fs15}\NAnd I admire your loyalty to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.11,0:58:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但那不是劝阻我的理由{\fs15}\NBut it does not dissuade me from my course.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.63,0:58:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你挑起的 米斯兰迪尔{\fs15}\NYou started this, Mithrandir.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.00,0:58:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我打完这场仗  你要原谅我{\fs15}\NYou will forgive me if I finish it!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.15,0:58:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,弓箭手准备好了吗{\fs15}\NAre the archers in position?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.39,0:58:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 国王 - 下命令{\fs15}\NYes, My Lord. - Give the order...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.22,0:58:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,看到任何东西在山上活动 格杀勿论{\fs15}\Nif anything moves on that mountain, kill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.82,0:58:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,矮人来的不是时候{\fs15}\NThe Dwarves are out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.94,0:59:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你 弓箭手{\fs15}\NYou, bowman!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.22,0:59:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你同不同意这样{\fs15}\NDid you agree with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.49,0:59:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,黄金对你就有那么重要吗{\fs15}\NIs gold so important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.04,0:59:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,难到你想用矮人的血换得黄金{\fs15}\NWould you buy it with the blood of Dwarves?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.79,0:59:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不会发生那样的事{\fs15}\NIt will not come to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.08,0:59:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这场仗他们无法取胜 - 他们不会罢手的{\fs15}\NThis is a fight they cannot win. - That won't stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.11,0:59:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为矮人会认输 不会{\fs15}\NYou think the Dwarves will surrender? They won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.27,0:59:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会为自己战斗至死{\fs15}\NThey will fight to the death to defend their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.36,0:59:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,比尔博・巴金斯{\fs15}\NBilbo Baggins!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.61,0:59:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我没搞错 他就是在守卫的眼皮底下{\fs15}\NIf I'm not mistaken, this is the Halfling who stole...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.51,0:59:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,偷走我地下室钥匙的半人吧{\fs15}\Nthe keys to my dungeons from under the nose of my guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.92,0:59:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是的{\fs15}\NHe is.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.02,0:59:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉那样做{\fs15}\NSorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.15,0:59:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我来是给你这个的{\fs15}\NI came to give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.34,0:59:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,孤山至尊{\fs15}\NThe Heart of the Mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.01,1:00:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,国王的宝石{\fs15}\NThe King's jewel.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.45,1:00:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,值很大一笔钱{\fs15}\NAnd worth a king's ransom.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.78,1:00:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的吗{\fs15}\NHow is this yours to give?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.14,1:00:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,作为财宝分额的十四分之一分给我的{\fs15}\NI took it as my 14th share of the treasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.92,1:00:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要拿给我{\fs15}\NWhy would you do this?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.14,1:00:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你对我们没有忠诚可言{\fs15}\NYou owe us no loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.61,1:00:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是为了你{\fs15}\NI'm not doing it for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.19,1:00:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道矮人都十分倔{\fs15}\NI know that Dwarves can be obstinate...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.13,1:00:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,顽固还有{\fs15}\Nand pigheaded and...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.47,1:00:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,难缠{\fs15}\Ndifficult.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.38,1:00:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以想象到他们多疑{\fs15}\NAnd suspicious and secretive...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.35,1:00:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,做事偷偷摸摸 没有礼貌{\fs15}\Nwith the worst manners you can possibly
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.16,1:00:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他们也很勇敢{\fs15}\Nimagine, but they are also brave...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.42,1:00:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,和善{\fs15}\Nand kind...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.56,1:00:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,还是依然顽固{\fs15}\Nand loyal to a fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.83,1:00:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我很喜欢他们 如果可以  我想救救他们{\fs15}\NI've grown very fond of them, and I would save them if I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.81,1:00:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但 索林{\fs15}\NBut Thorin...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.66,1:00:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他珍视这个宝石胜过一切{\fs15}\Nvalues this stone above all else.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.22,1:00:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,作为宝石回归的交换 我想他会{\fs15}\NIn exchange for it's return, I believe he will...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.80,1:00:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,给你们约定好的 没有必要再去{\fs15}\Ngive you what you were owed. There will be no need...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.38,1:00:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,打一仗{\fs15}\Nfor war.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.02,1:00:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚在此休息{\fs15}\NRest up tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.00,1:00:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你明天必须离开 - 什么{\fs15}\NYou must leave on the morrow. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.94,1:01:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,走得越远越好{\fs15}\NGet as far away from here as possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.74,1:01:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我 是不会离开的 - 哦{\fs15}\N- I-I'm not leaving. - Oh?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.49,1:01:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你把我选中为14人中的一个{\fs15}\NYou picked me as the 14th man.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.17,1:01:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我还不想离开我的同伴{\fs15}\NI'm not about to leave the company now.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.41,1:01:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这里没有同伴 再也没有了{\fs15}\NThere is no company, not any more.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.64,1:01:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不想去想索林会做什么{\fs15}\NAnd I don't like to think what Thorin would do...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.18,1:01:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,当他发现你做的事后{\fs15}\Nwhen he finds out what you've done.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.70,1:01:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我不害怕索林{\fs15}\NI'm not afraid of Thorin.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.96,1:01:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  你应该害怕{\fs15}\NWell, you should be.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.48,1:01:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不要低估了{\fs15}\NDon't underestimate...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.06,1:01:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,来自黄金的邪恶{\fs15}\Nthe evil of gold.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.56,1:01:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,黄金{\fs15}\NGold...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.47,1:01:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,会在狡猾之人心中留下遐思{\fs15}\Nover which a serpent had long brooded.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.84,1:01:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,恶龙的呕吐物会渗透到所有{\fs15}\NDragon-sickness seeps into the hearts of all who get...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.50,1:01:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,靠近孤山的人{\fs15}\Nnear this Mountain.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.11,1:01:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,无人幸免{\fs15}\NAlmost all.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.71,1:01:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你{\fs15}\NYou there!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.33,1:01:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,给矮人找个床{\fs15}\NFind this Hobbit a bed...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.61,1:01:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,准备热食填饱他的肚子{\fs15}\Nand fill his belly with hot food.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.72,1:01:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他应得的{\fs15}\NHe has earned it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.91,1:01:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 留意他{\fs15}\NHey, keep an eye on him.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.72,1:01:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他想离开 告诉我{\fs15}\NIf he should try to leave, you tell me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.55,1:01:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,快走 蠢矮人{\fs15}\NMove it, stupid Hobbit.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.60,1:02:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒 醒醒 矮人 还没有 起来{\fs15}\NWakey, Wakey. Hobbit, up you... get?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.97,1:02:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,下次就会射在你的头上{\fs15}\NI will put the next one between your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.67,1:03:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是来告诉你{\fs15}\NWe've come to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.47,1:03:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,承诺给你的报答{\fs15}\Npayment of your debt has been offered...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.76,1:03:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,接受你的提议{\fs15}\Nand accepte d.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.95,1:03:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,什么报答{\fs15}\NWhat payment?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.10,1:03:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都不会给你{\fs15}\NI gave you nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.14,1:03:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你们什么都没有{\fs15}\NYou have nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.77,1:03:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有这个{\fs15}\NWe have this.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.20,1:03:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他们拿着传家宝钻{\fs15}\NThey have the Arkenstone.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.12,1:03:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,盗贼{\fs15}\NThieves.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.30,1:03:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么从我们这里拿到传家宝的{\fs15}\NHow came you by the heirloom of our house?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.29,1:03:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这块宝石属于{\fs15}\NThat stone belongs to...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.79,1:03:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,国王{\fs15}\Nthe king.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.55,1:03:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,国王想要拿到{\fs15}\NAnd the King may have it...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.63,1:04:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,也是我们说了算{\fs15}\Nand our good will.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.97,1:04:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但首先他得履行他得诺言{\fs15}\NBut first he must honour his word.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.37,1:04:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他们以为我们是傻子{\fs15}\NThey're taking us for fools.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.52,1:04:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是他们的计谋{\fs15}\NThis is a ruse...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.49,1:04:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不堪入耳的谎言{\fs15}\Nand a filthy lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.80,1:04:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,阿肯宝钻还在孤山上 你们在使诈{\fs15}\NThe Arkenstone is in this Mountain, it is a trick!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.25,1:04:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是诡计{\fs15}\NI-It's no trick.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.93,1:04:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,宝石是真的{\fs15}\NThe stone is real...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.02,1:04:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我给他们的{\fs15}\NI gave it to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.29,1:04:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是你{\fs15}\NYou?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.10,1:04:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,只是作为我应得的那一份{\fs15}\NI took it as my 14th share.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.52,1:04:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你从我这里偷走{\fs15}\NYou would steel from me?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.13,1:04:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,从你这里偷走 不{\fs15}\NSteel from you? No,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.80,1:04:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 我也许是个窃贼 但我自认为我是一个诚实的人{\fs15}\Nno. I may be a burglar, but I like to think I'm an honest one.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.94,1:05:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴我的要求能让你把我抓起来{\fs15}\NI'm willing to let it stand against my claim.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.05,1:05:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你的要求{\fs15}\NAgainst your claim?
