Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.36,1:06:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,作为孤山之王{\fs15}\NYou're not making a very splendid figure
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.75,1:06:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你从没有做过什么辉煌的事迹{\fs15}\Nas King under the Mountain,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.40,1:06:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你做过吗 索林{\fs15}\Nare you, Thorin,
