Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.12,1:06:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,传家宝石给你{\fs15}\NThe return of the...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.58,1:06:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,作为你兑现你诺言的条件{\fs15}\NArkenstone for what was promised.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.20,1:06:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,快给我们答案{\fs15}\NGive us your answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.14,1:06:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你是想要和平{\fs15}\NWill you have peace...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.42,1:06:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,还是战争{\fs15}\Nor war?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.77,1:07:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我要战争{\fs15}\NI will have war.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.34,1:07:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,铁足{\fs15}\NIronfoot.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.33,1:07:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,丹恩 丹恩{\fs15}\NDáin! Dáin!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.26,1:07:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,丹恩{\fs15}\NDáin!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.25,1:07:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那是谁  看起来可不友善{\fs15}\NWho is that? He doesn't look very happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.37,1:07:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是丹恩 铁丘陵之王{\fs15}\NIt is Dáin, Lord of the Iron Hills.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.99,1:08:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,索林的表哥 - 他们相像吗{\fs15}\NThorin's cousin. - Are they alike?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.38,1:08:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我越来越觉得索林有两个{\fs15}\NI've always found Thorin the more reasonable of the two.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.11,1:08:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好{\fs15}\NGood morning!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.49,1:08:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都还好吧{\fs15}\NHow are we all?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.81,1:08:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个小提议{\fs15}\NI have a wee proposition,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.54,1:08:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不介意给我一点{\fs15}\Nif you wouldn't mind giving me a few moments...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.78,1:08:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你宝贵的时间{\fs15}\Nof your time.
