Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.61,1:08:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,都{\fs15}\NJUST...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.37,1:08:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑吧{\fs15}\NSODDING OFF?!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.04,1:08:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人{\fs15}\NAll of you!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.19,1:08:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,现在{\fs15}\NRight now!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.90,1:08:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不要后退{\fs15}\NStand fast!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.70,1:08:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静一下 丹恩大王{\fs15}\NCalm now, Lord Dáin.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.07,1:08:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 灰袍子甘道夫{\fs15}\N- Gandalf the Grey.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.52,1:08:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,叫这群乌合之众{\fs15}\NTell this rabble to leave
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.71,1:08:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我会{\fs15}\Nor I'll...
