Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.01,1:08:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没有必要{\fs15}\NThere is no need for...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.32,1:08:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,发起矮人 人类 精灵之间的战争{\fs15}\Nwar between Dwarves, Men and Elves.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.44,1:09:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,一大批的半兽人{\fs15}\NA legion of Orcs...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.52,1:09:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,正在朝孤山赶来{\fs15}\Nmarch on the Mountain.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.31,1:09:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,叫你的人退下{\fs15}\NStand your army down.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.26,1:09:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不会再任何精灵面前退缩{\fs15}\N- I will not stand down before any Elf.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.56,1:09:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其在这块没有信念的精灵之地{\fs15}\NNot least this faithless woodland sprite.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.23,1:09:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他一心想凌驾在我的人民之上{\fs15}\NHe wishes nothing but ill upon my people.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.23,1:09:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他{\fs15}\NIf he...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.42,1:09:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,依然选择和我们对抗{\fs15}\Nchooses to stand between me and my kin,
