Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.50,1:09:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那就看看他是不是还那样傻{\fs15}\NSee if he's still smirking then.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.57,1:09:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 丹恩{\fs15}\N- Dáin!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.98,1:09:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他完全疯了 和他堂弟一样{\fs15}\NHe's clearly mad, like his cousin.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.07,1:09:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你也听到了 小子 我们上{\fs15}\NYou hear that, lads? We're on!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.78,1:09:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们给这些杂种漂亮的一锤{\fs15}\NLet's give these bastards a good hammering.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.41,1:09:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,虫人{\fs15}\NWere-worms!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.78,1:10:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 别这样{\fs15}\NOh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.92,1:10:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,出来吧  我的军队
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.17,1:10:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,居然是一大堆虫{\fs15}\NThe Hordes of Hell are...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.93,1:10:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,跑到我们上面{\fs15}\Nupon us!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.39,1:10:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,上阵 上阵  都灵之子{\fs15}\NTo battle, to battle, sons of Durin!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.31,1:10:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我要出去打仗 谁和我一起去{\fs15}\NI'm going over the wall, who's coming with me?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.41,1:10:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好 是 快点 我们走{\fs15}\NAye! Yes! Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.49,1:10:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,站住 - 什么{\fs15}\NStand down. - What?
