Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.89,1:11:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,精灵们{\fs15}\NThe Elves,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.03,1:11:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不去战斗吗{\fs15}\Nwill they not fight?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.78,1:11:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,瑟兰迪尔{\fs15}\NThranduil!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.85,1:11:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这太疯狂了{\fs15}\NThis is madness!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.71,1:12:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 甘道夫{\fs15}\NUh, Gandalf...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.90,1:12:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这个地方会守得住吗{\fs15}\Nis this a good place to stand?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.19,1:12:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,派出兽人{\fs15}\Nsend in the war beast
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.39,1:12:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他们抵挡不住两面夹击{\fs15}\Nthe cannt fight on two fronts
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.76,1:12:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们开始行动{\fs15}\Nnow  we make our move
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.57,1:12:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,进攻城市{\fs15}\Nattack the city
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.65,1:12:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,阿索格{\fs15}\NAzog.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.69,1:12:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他想把我们分开{\fs15}\NHe's trying to cut us off.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.93,1:13:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的人{\fs15}\NAll of you...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.99,1:13:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,退回到河谷戴尔{\fs15}\Nfall back to Dale!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.16,1:13:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,快{\fs15}\NNow!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.20,1:13:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,到城里去 比尔博 这边{\fs15}\NTo the city! Bilbo, this way!
