Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.72,1:14:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂尔达{\fs15}\NTilda!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.23,1:14:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子 我的孩子在哪里{\fs15}\NMy children, where are my children?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.22,1:14:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我看见过 刚才在老市场下面{\fs15}\NI saw them, they were down in the Old Market.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.37,1:14:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,市场 那现在在哪里{\fs15}\NThe Market? Where are they now?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.65,1:14:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,西格莉德 蒂尔达{\fs15}\NTilda! Sigrid!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.55,1:14:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,巴德 半兽人涌进了堤道{\fs15}\NBard, Orcs are storming over the Causeway.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.55,1:14:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,带弓箭手到东面的防护栏{\fs15}\NGet the bowmen to the eastern parapet.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.48,1:14:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,抵挡得越久越好{\fs15}\NHold them of for as long as you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.66,1:14:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,弓箭手 跟我来{\fs15}\NArchers, this way!
