Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.35,1:15:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,向前冲 前进 战斗至死{\fs15}\NCharge! Onward! To the death!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.98,1:16:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲 父亲{\fs15}\NDa! - Da!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.83,1:16:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里 - 父亲在哪里{\fs15}\NOver here! - Da is here!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.68,1:16:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂尔达{\fs15}\NTilda!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.93,1:16:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,贝恩{\fs15}\NBain!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.08,1:16:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,西格莉德 快趴下{\fs15}\NSigrid! Get down!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.33,1:17:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  你去把孩子和女人聚集起来{\fs15}\NListen, I need you to gather the women and children,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.94,1:17:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,带他们到大会堂去{\fs15}\Ntake them to the Great Hall...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.54,1:17:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,把门口挡住{\fs15}\Nand barricade the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.33,1:17:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吗 不管什么原因都不要出来{\fs15}\NYou understand? You must not come out for any reason.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.29,1:17:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们要和你在一起{\fs15}\N- We want to stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.86,1:17:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,对你的父亲尊敬点{\fs15}\NShow your father some respect.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.12,1:17:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你把他交给我 镇长{\fs15}\NYou leave it to me, Sire.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.75,1:17:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你听到他说的了 我们去大会堂{\fs15}\NYou heard him, we make for Great Hall.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.54,1:17:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,艾福德 只是女人和小孩  我需要每一个男人来打仗{\fs15}\NAlfrid, women and children only. I need every man fighting.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.09,1:17:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你会回来 - 我会保证他们安全的 镇长{\fs15}\NSee that you return. - I'll get them to safety, Sire.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.57,1:17:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我的剑就是你的命令{\fs15}\NMy sword is yours to command.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.15,1:17:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,快起来{\fs15}\NGet up!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.53,1:17:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,照顾好他们 - 我会的{\fs15}\NLook after them. - I will.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.32,1:17:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 老婆婆{\fs15}\NShift it, granny.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.95,1:17:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,快去大会堂{\fs15}\NMake for the Great Hall.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.33,1:17:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,别挡我的路{\fs15}\NOut of my way!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.80,1:18:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不要管那些瘸子{\fs15}\NAbandon the cripples!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.63,1:18:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他们守不住这座城
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.34,1:18:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,矮人快要死光了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.17,1:19:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你个杂种{\fs15}\NYou buggers!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.05,1:19:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,索林{\fs15}\NThorin!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.77,1:19:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,索林在哪里{\fs15}\NWhere's Thorin?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.18,1:19:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要他 他在哪里{\fs15}\NWe need him. Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.33,1:19:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,让这里血染大地
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.60,1:19:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,杀光他们
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.41,1:19:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,后退{\fs15}\NPull back!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.10,1:20:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们什么时候开始不管{\fs15}\NSince when do we forsake our...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.93,1:20:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,自己人的死活了{\fs15}\Nown people?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.45,1:20:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,索林 他们在外面要战死了{\fs15}\NThorin, they are dying out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.37,1:20:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,要战死了{\fs15}\Nout there.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.04,1:20:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,孤山上有很多墙{\fs15}\NThere are halls beneath halls within this Mountain,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.49,1:20:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,需要我们加强防护{\fs15}\Nplaces we can fortify.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.72,1:20:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,加固 保证我们安全吗{\fs15}\NShore up, make safe?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.52,1:20:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是的{\fs15}\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.92,1:20:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是{\fs15}\NYes,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.03,1:20:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那样{\fs15}\Nthat is it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.88,1:20:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得把黄金移到更深的地下{\fs15}\NWe must move the gold further underground...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.83,1:20:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,保证它们安全 -  你到底有没有听我说{\fs15}\Nto safety. - Did you not hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.43,1:20:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,多恩被重重包围{\fs15}\NDáin is surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.87,1:20:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他们快被杀光了 索林{\fs15}\NThey're being slaughtered, Thorin.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.40,1:20:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,许多已经战死{\fs15}\NMany die in war,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.06,1:20:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,生命如此贫贱{\fs15}\Nlive is cheap.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.70,1:20:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但是财宝{\fs15}\NBut a treasure...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.74,1:20:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,却如此{\fs15}\Nsuch as this...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.97,1:20:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就连生命的逝去都比不上{\fs15}\Ncannot be counted in lives lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.67,1:21:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,它值得我们所有人流血牺牲{\fs15}\NIt is worth all the blood we can spend.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.76,1:21:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你戴着王冠冠冕堂皇的坐在这里{\fs15}\NYou sit here in these vast halls with a crown upon your head,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.73,1:21:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,已没有了你当年的雄风{\fs15}\Nand yet you are lesser now than you have ever been.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.11,1:21:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这样说得 我好像是一个卑贱的矮人国王{\fs15}\NDo not speak to me as if I were some lowly DwarfLord.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.35,1:21:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,原来{\fs15}\NAs is if...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.14,1:21:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我仍然是{\fs15}\NI were still...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.89,1:21:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,索林・橡木盾{\fs15}\NThorin... Oakenshield.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.70,1:21:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你的国王 - 你永远都是我的国王{\fs15}\NI am your King! - You were always my King.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.53,1:21:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你过去一直都是{\fs15}\NYou used to know that once.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.29,1:21:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你没看见你自己变成了什么样子{\fs15}\NYou cannot see what you have become.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.23,1:21:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,滚{\fs15}\NGo,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.19,1:21:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,出去{\fs15}\Nget out...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.99,1:22:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,趁我还没杀你{\fs15}\Nbefore I kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.06,1:22:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你戴着王冠冠冕堂皇的坐在这里{\fs15}\N{\i1}You sit here with a crown upon your head.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.69,1:22:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你已没有了你当年的雄风{\fs15}\N{\i1}You are lesser now than you have ever been.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.19,1:22:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,生命的逝去换不来财宝的珍贵{\fs15}\N{\i1}A treasure such as this cannot be counted in lives lost.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.20,1:22:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,财宝上全是呕吐物{\fs15}\N{\i1}A sickness lies upon that treasure.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.66,1:22:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,孤山之王的盲目自大{\fs15}\N{\i1}The blind ambition of a Mountain King.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.94,1:22:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,难道我不配当国王{\fs15}\N{\i1}Am I not the King?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.56,1:22:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,黄金是我们的 也只属于我们{\fs15}\N{\i1}This gold is ours, and ours alone.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.01,1:22:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,储存的财宝{\fs15}\N{\i1}Treasure hoard...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.47,1:22:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会将{\fs15}\N{\i1}I will not part...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.83,1:22:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,一分钱分出去{\fs15}\N{\i1}with a single coin.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.74,1:22:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他看不到他内心深处的欲望{\fs15}\N{\i1}He could not see beyond his own desire!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.34,1:22:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我是低贱的矮人{\fs15}\N{\i1}As if I were some lowly Dwarf Lord.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.09,1:22:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,索林・橡木盾{\fs15}\N{\i1}Thorin Oakenshield.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.66,1:22:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,呕吐物把你的祖父逼疯了{\fs15}\N{\i1}A sickness which drove your grandfather mad.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.54,1:22:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,橡木盾{\fs15}\N{\i1}Oakenshield.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.65,1:23:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我是索林 索恩之子 索尔之子{\fs15}\N{\i1}This is Thorin, son of Thráin, son of Thrór.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.48,1:23:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我的祖父{\fs15}\N{\i1}I am not my grandfather.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.81,1:23:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你是都灵的王位继承人{\fs15}\N{\i1}You are the heir to the Throne of Durin.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.78,1:23:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他们快死了{\fs15}\N{\i1}They are dying out there.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.64,1:23:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,夺回埃雷博{\fs15}\N{\i1}Take back Erebor.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.41,1:23:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,丹恩被重重围住{\fs15}\N{\i1}Dáin is surrounded.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.31,1:23:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,被围住{\fs15}\N{\i1}Is surrounded.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.44,1:23:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,夺回你的家园{\fs15}\N{\i1}Take back your homeland.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.27,1:23:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你变了 索林{\fs15}\N{\i1}You are changed, Thorin.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.54,1:23:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是祖父{\fs15}\N{\i1}I'm not my grandfather.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.46,1:23:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,难道财宝真的比你的荣耀值钱{\fs15}\N{\i1}Is this treasure truly worth more than your honour?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.74,1:23:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是祖父{\fs15}\N{\i1}I'm not my grandfather.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.74,1:23:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,财宝会导致你的死亡{\fs15}\N{\i1}This treasure will be your death.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.28,1:24:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,后撤{\fs15}\NFall back!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.45,1:24:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,后撤 撤到孤山上{\fs15}\NFall back! Back to the Mountain!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.61,1:24:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,后退{\fs15}\NFall back!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.35,1:24:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的死期到了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.15,1:24:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,准备最后的攻击
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.73,1:25:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会再{\fs15}\NI will not hide...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.35,1:25:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,躲在这些石头后面了{\fs15}\Nbehind a wall of stone,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.50,1:25:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,其它人还在外面为我们而战{\fs15}\Nwhile others fight our battles for us!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.54,1:25:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们生来不是这样的 索林{\fs15}\NIt is not in my blood, Thorin.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.05,1:25:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是{\fs15}\NNo,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.40,1:25:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这样的{\fs15}\Nit is not.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.21,1:25:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是都灵之子{\fs15}\NWe are sons of Durin...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.40,1:25:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,身为都灵的族人{\fs15}\Nand Durin's folk...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.25,1:25:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不会从战斗中逃跑{\fs15}\Ndo not flee from a fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.51,1:26:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经没有权力要求你们{\fs15}\NI have no right to ask this of any of you,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.57,1:26:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你们愿意和我一起最后一战吗{\fs15}\Nbut will you follow me one last time?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.69,1:26:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,还不到时候  等等  等等
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.24,1:26:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 进攻
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.41,1:27:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,索林{\fs15}\NThorin.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.77,1:27:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,跟着国王 跟着{\fs15}\NTo the King! To the...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.84,1:27:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,国王{\fs15}\NKing!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.53,1:28:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那些矮人{\fs15}\NThe Dwarves,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.72,1:28:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在重整{\fs15}\Nthey're rallying.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.48,1:28:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,和他们的国王一起{\fs15}\NThey're rallying to their King.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.97,1:28:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,有谁不怕死的 跟我来{\fs15}\NAny man who wants to give their last follow me!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.00,1:28:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我看见男人们为我们出生入死{\fs15}\NI say we stand with our men in life and in death.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.51,1:28:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我也去 - 带上武器{\fs15}\N- I'm with ya. - Arm yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.34,1:28:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,和我们一起吧 亲爱的 - 不 不  不{\fs15}\NCome with us, love. - No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.00,1:28:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你就让我一个老人在这里吧 - 不要害怕{\fs15}\NYou leave an old woman be. - Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.49,1:28:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫你滚开{\fs15}\NI said get off!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.77,1:28:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是马屁精艾福德啊{\fs15}\NAlfrid Lickspittle,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.35,1:28:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是一个懦夫- 懦夫{\fs15}\Nyou are a coward. - A Coward?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.79,1:29:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,并不是每一个男人都有胆穿着女人的束胸衣{\fs15}\NNot every man is brave enough to wear a corset.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.57,1:29:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你不配当男人{\fs15}\NYou're not a man,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.89,1:29:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你是 黄鼠狼{\fs15}\Nyou're a weasel.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.27,1:29:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,多恩{\fs15}\NDáin!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.85,1:29:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,索林 撑住{\fs15}\NThorin... hold on!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.30,1:29:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我来了{\fs15}\NI'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.29,1:29:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 表弟{\fs15}\NHey, cousin...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.37,1:29:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这么久才来{\fs15}\Nwhat took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.96,1:29:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这些讨厌的家伙太多了 索林{\fs15}\NThere's too many of these buggers, Thorin.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.23,1:29:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你有个计划{\fs15}\NI hope you've got a plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.61,1:29:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,对{\fs15}\NAye,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.61,1:29:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要去杀掉他们的首领{\fs15}\Nwe're going to take out their leader.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.00,1:29:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,阿索格{\fs15}\NAzog?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.61,1:29:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去杀了那个肮脏污秽的东西{\fs15}\NI'm going to kill that piece of filth.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.76,1:29:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我冲{\fs15}\NLead on!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.83,1:30:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可能会活着{\fs15}\NWe may yet survive this.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.49,1:30:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,甘道夫{\fs15}\NGandalf!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.11,1:30:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是索林{\fs15}\NIt's Thorin.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.92,1:30:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,菲力和奇力{\fs15}\NAnd Fíli and Kíli...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.99,1:30:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,还有德瓦林{\fs15}\Nand Dwalin.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.79,1:30:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他带着最勇猛的勇士{\fs15}\NHe's taking his best warriors.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.00,1:30:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,去干什么{\fs15}\NTo do what?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.53,1:30:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,去砍掉那脏东西的头{\fs15}\NTo cut the head of the snake.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.25,1:31:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,去死吧{\fs15}\NDie!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.29,1:31:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,甘道夫{\fs15}\NGandalf!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.90,1:31:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,莱戈拉斯{\fs15}\NLegolas.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.20,1:31:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,绿叶精灵莱戈拉斯 - 还有第二队敌军{\fs15}\NLegolas Greenleaf! - There's a second army.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.29,1:31:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,博尔格领导了冈达巴山的半兽人{\fs15}\NBolg leads a force of Gundabad Orcs.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.37,1:31:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,快赶上我们了{\fs15}\NThey are almost upon us.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.47,1:31:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,冈达巴山 啊 这就是他们一直计划的事{\fs15}\NGundabad? Ahh. This was their plan all along.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.34,1:31:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,阿索格消耗我们得主力 博尔格就从北方扫荡{\fs15}\NAzog engages our forces, then Bolg sweeps in from the north.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.05,1:31:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 从 北方{\fs15}\NWhat, th... the north?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.70,1:31:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,哪边是北方{\fs15}\NWhere is the north...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.25,1:31:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,到底在哪里  - 在渡鸦岭{\fs15}\Nexactly? - Ravenhill.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.60,1:31:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,渡鸦岭{\fs15}\NRavenhill?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.84,1:31:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,索林还在那上面{\fs15}\NThorin is up there...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.74,1:31:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,还有菲力和奇力 都在那上面{\fs15}\Nand Fíli and Kíli. They're all up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.24,1:32:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪里{\fs15}\NWhere is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.88,1:32:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来是空的{\fs15}\NIt looks empty.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.14,1:32:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为阿索格逃跑了  - 我不那样想{\fs15}\NI think Azog has fled. - I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.13,1:32:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,菲力{\fs15}\NFíli,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.20,1:32:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,带上你的兄弟{\fs15}\Ntake your brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.62,1:32:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,在塔下面搜寻一番{\fs15}\NScout out the towers.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.10,1:32:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,低姿前行注意观察  如果你发现了什么{\fs15}\NKeep low and out of sight. If you see something,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.06,1:32:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,立即回来报告 不要交战 明白了吗{\fs15}\Nreport back, do not engage. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.51,1:32:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有麻烦了 哥布林佣兵{\fs15}\NWe have company. Goblin mercenaries.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.53,1:32:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不超过一百个 - 我们会好好招待他们的 走{\fs15}\NNo more then a hundred. - We'll take care of them. Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.99,1:32:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,快走{\fs15}\NGo!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.65,1:33:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,召回你的同伴{\fs15}\NRecall your company.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.47,1:33:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,大王 把军力派遣到渡鸦岭吧{\fs15}\NMy Lord, disperse this force to Ravenhill,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.17,1:33:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,矮人们快要扛不住了{\fs15}\Nthe Dwarves are about to be overrun.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.39,1:33:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,索林必须得到警告  - 想办法 警告他吧{\fs15}\NThorin must be warned. - By all means, warn him.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.88,1:33:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经在这片诅咒之地流了太多血{\fs15}\NI've spent enough Elvish blood in defence of this accursed land.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.49,1:33:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不能再流了{\fs15}\NNo more!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.11,1:33:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,瑟兰迪尔{\fs15}\NThranduil?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.74,1:33:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我去 - 不要做蠢事{\fs15}\NI'll go. - Don't be ridiculous,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.91,1:33:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会成功的 - 为什么{\fs15}\Nyou'll never make it. - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.37,1:33:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们会看见你过去 并杀了你{\fs15}\NBecause they will see you coming, and kill you!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.85,1:33:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不 他们不会{\fs15}\NNo, they won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.31,1:33:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他们看不见我{\fs15}\NThey won't see me.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.87,1:34:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这是不可能的  我不准许{\fs15}\NIt's out of the question. I won't allow it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.57,1:34:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是在请求得到你的准许 甘道夫{\fs15}\NI'm not asking you to allow it, Gandalf.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.18,1:34:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,噢{\fs15}\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.71,1:34:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能再走了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.44,1:34:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不能走开不管 这次不行{\fs15}\NYou will not turn away. Not this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.57,1:34:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,别挡我的路{\fs15}\NGet out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.40,1:34:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,矮人会被屠杀殆尽{\fs15}\NThe Dwarves will be slaughtered.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.24,1:34:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是 他们都会死{\fs15}\NYes, they will die.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.54,1:34:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,今天 或许明天{\fs15}\NToday... tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.52,1:35:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,一年或者一百年之后早晚都会死{\fs15}\None year hence a hundred years from now
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.27,1:35:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那又有什么关系呢{\fs15}\NWhat does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.46,1:35:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都是凡人{\fs15}\NThey are mortal.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.17,1:35:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为你的生命就比他们高贵些{\fs15}\NYou think your life is worth more than theirs,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.26,1:35:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,难道就没有一点点爱吗{\fs15}\Nwhile there is no love in it?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.48,1:35:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,对于你来说 没有{\fs15}\NThere is no love in you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.76,1:35:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你是如何看待爱的 什么都不是{\fs15}\NWhat do you know of love? Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.00,1:35:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你对那个矮人的感情不是真的{\fs15}\NWhat you feel for that Dwarf is not real.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.96,1:35:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为那是爱 那你准备为它而死了吗{\fs15}\NYou think it is love? Are you ready to die for it?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.10,1:35:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你要伤害她
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.98,1:35:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那你先杀了我
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.22,1:35:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你一起去{\fs15}\NI will go with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.60,1:36:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,起来{\fs15}\NGet up.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.02,1:36:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,离我远一点 我不会听从{\fs15}\NGet away from me. I don't take orders...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.30,1:36:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你的命令 人们相信你{\fs15}\Nfrom you. People trusted you,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.05,1:36:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他们才会听从你{\fs15}\Nthey listened to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.44,1:36:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,镇长的的壁炉架{\fs15}\NThe Master's mantel...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.78,1:36:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就在那里唾手可得{\fs15}\Nwas there for the taking...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.87,1:36:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,而你却放任不管{\fs15}\Nand you threw it all away.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.51,1:36:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,为了什么{\fs15}\NFor what?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.28,1:36:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,艾福德{\fs15}\NAlfrid,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.52,1:36:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好跑快点{\fs15}\Nyour slip is showing.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.35,1:37:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,待在这里 到下面去找{\fs15}\NStay here, search the lower levels.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.12,1:37:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我来搞定这里{\fs15}\NI've got this.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.94,1:37:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,半兽人军队在哪里{\fs15}\NWhere is that Orc-filth?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.96,1:37:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,索林{\fs15}\NThorin!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.51,1:37:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,比尔博{\fs15}\NBilbo.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.95,1:37:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你们必须离开这里 现在{\fs15}\NYou have to leave here. Now!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.97,1:37:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,阿索格还有一支军队 正在从北面进攻{\fs15}\NAzog has another army, attacking from the north.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.98,1:37:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,t望塔已经被完全围住了{\fs15}\NThis watchtower will be completely surrounded,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.94,1:37:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,没有逃出去的路了  - 我们如此之近{\fs15}\Nthere'll be no way out. - We are so close.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.93,1:37:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那些半兽人败类就在里面{\fs15}\NThat Orc-scum is in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.52,1:37:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我建议冲进去 - 不{\fs15}\NI say we push on. - No!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.45,1:37:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那正是他们想要的  他想引我们进去{\fs15}\NThat's what he wants. He wants to draw us in.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.82,1:37:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个圈套{\fs15}\NThis is a trap.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.01,1:37:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,找到菲力和奇力 叫他们回来{\fs15}\NFind Fíli and Kíli, call them back.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.03,1:37:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,索林 你真的要这么做吗 - 快去{\fs15}\NThorin, are you sure about this? - Do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.93,1:38:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们改日再和他一战{\fs15}\NWe live to fight another day.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.54,1:38:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 不{\fs15}\NOh no.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.30,1:38:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这个最先死
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.14,1:38:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,然后是他的兄弟
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.56,1:38:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,再就是你 橡木盾
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.52,1:38:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你将是最后一个
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.49,1:38:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,快走{\fs15}\NGo.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.42,1:38:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑啊{\fs15}\NRun!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.95,1:38:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这里就是你死的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.61,1:39:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,奇力{\fs15}\NKíli!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.62,1:39:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,索林{\fs15}\NThorin!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.75,1:39:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,索林 不要{\fs15}\NThorin, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.23,1:40:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,杀光他们
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.79,1:40:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不{\fs15}\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.08,1:41:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,奇力{\fs15}\NKíli!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.72,1:42:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,快去杀戮吧
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.48,1:42:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了他
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.29,1:43:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,奇力{\fs15}\NKíli!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.38,1:43:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,奇力{\fs15}\NKíli!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.54,1:43:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,塔瑞尔 - 奇力{\fs15}\NTauriel! - Kíli.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.04,1:44:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不要{\fs15}\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.72,1:44:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不{\fs15}\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.93,1:49:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,塔瑞尔{\fs15}\NTauriel!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.25,1:54:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,老鹰来了{\fs15}\NThe eagles are coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.23,1:55:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 比尔博{\fs15}\NHey, Bilbo.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:20.28,1:55:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不要看 不要动 安静的躺着{\fs15}\NNo, don't look. Don't move. Lie still.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:23.94,1:55:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,噢{\fs15}\NOw.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:27.07,1:55:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴你在这里 - 嘘 嘘 嘘 嘘{\fs15}\NI'm glad you're here. - Shh, shh, shh, shh.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.99,1:55:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我想向我们的友谊告别{\fs15}\NI wish to part from you in friendship. - No,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.81,1:55:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你哪里也不会去 索林{\fs15}\Nyou are not going anywhere, Thorin,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.46,1:55:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你会活下去的{\fs15}\Nyou're going to live.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.97,1:55:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我收回在城门口对你说的话和做的事{\fs15}\NI would take back my words and my deeds at the gate.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:42.38,1:55:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你做了真正朋友之间才会做的事{\fs15}\NYou did what only a true friend would do.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.84,1:55:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,原谅我{\fs15}\NForgive me.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.45,1:55:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,以前是我视若不见{\fs15}\NI was too blind to see.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:55.04,1:56:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常抱歉让你陷入如此境地{\fs15}\NI am so sorry that I have led you into such peril.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.76,1:56:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不 - 我很高心与你共进退 索林{\fs15}\NNo, I-I'm glad to have shared in your perils, Thorin.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:03.87,1:56:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,包括他们中的每一个人{\fs15}\NEach and every one of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:08.55,1:56:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,很多巴金斯人求都求不来的{\fs15}\NIt is far more than any Baggins deserves.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.54,1:56:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,永别了  聪明的小偷{\fs15}\NFarewell, Master Burglar.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.60,1:56:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,回去坐在你的小椅子上写着书{\fs15}\NGo back to your books and your armchair.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:28.19,1:56:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,种几棵树{\fs15}\NPlant your trees,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:30.69,1:56:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,看着它们长大{\fs15}\Nwatch them grow.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:37.78,1:56:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,如果更多的人珍惜家园{\fs15}\NIf more people valued home...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:42.19,1:56:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,胜过黄金{\fs15}\Nabove gold,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.83,1:56:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那么这个世界会变得更加美丽{\fs15}\Nthis world would be a merrier place.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:52.42,1:56:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 不 不 不  不{\fs15}\NNo. No, no, no, no. No,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:54.95,1:56:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,索林{\fs15}\NThorin!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:56.28,1:56:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,索林 不准你{\fs15}\NThorin, don't you dare...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.85,1:57:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,索林{\fs15}\NThorin?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:06.66,1:57:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,看看 索林 索林  坚持住{\fs15}\NLook, Thorin. Thorin, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:09.78,1:57:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你要挺住{\fs15}\NYou hold on,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:10.78,1:57:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 鹰{\fs15}\Nyou see, the Eagles...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:12.45,1:57:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,鹰 鹰来帮助我们了{\fs15}\Nthe Eagles, the Eagles are here.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:15.38,1:57:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,索林{\fs15}\NThorin...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:20.10,1:57:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,鹰{\fs15}\Nthe Eagles...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:18.20,1:58:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我 不能回去{\fs15}\NI... can not go back.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:22.22,1:58:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那你要到哪里去{\fs15}\NWhere will you go?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:25.03,1:58:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道{\fs15}\NI do not know.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:27.72,1:58:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,去北方吧{\fs15}\NGo north.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:29.49,1:58:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,找到登丹人{\fs15}\NFind the Dúnedain.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:33.15,1:58:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那里有一个年轻的游骑兵 你应该见见他{\fs15}\NThere is a young ranger amongst them, you should meet him.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:38.09,1:58:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他的父亲亚拉松是一个好人{\fs15}\NHis father Arathorn was a good man.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:41.74,1:58:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,儿子可能会青出于蓝而胜于蓝{\fs15}\NHis son might grow to be a great one.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:48.06,1:58:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫什么名字{\fs15}\NWhat is his name?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:49.25,1:58:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,别人都叫他挺进者{\fs15}\NHe is known in the wild as Strider.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:52.13,1:58:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他的真实名字恐怕得你自己去发现了{\fs15}\NHis true name you must discover for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:01.80,1:59:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,莱戈拉斯 你母亲很爱你{\fs15}\NLegolas, your mother loved you,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:08.88,1:59:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,超越任何人 超越生命{\fs15}\Nmore than anyone, more than life.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:48.38,1:59:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想要埋葬他{\fs15}\NThey want to bury him.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:52.50,1:59:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是的{\fs15}\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:55.24,2:00:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这就是爱 我并不希望这样{\fs15}\NIf this is love, I do not want it.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:01.27,2:00:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,请相信我{\fs15}\NTake it from me, please?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:10.72,2:00:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会这么痛{\fs15}\NWhy does it hurt so much?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:13.64,2:00:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这都是真的{\fs15}\NBecause it was real.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:02.02,2:03:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚这里会有一场盛宴{\fs15}\NThere is to be a great feast tonight.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:04.63,2:03:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,人们会传唱 故事会流传{\fs15}\NSongs will be sung, tales will be told,
Dialogue: 0,2:03:09.76,2:03:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,索林・橡木盾{\fs15}\Nand Thorin Oakenshield...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:11.90,2:03:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,也将会成为传奇{\fs15}\Nwill pass into legend.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:16.29,2:03:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道现在你是有多尊敬他{\fs15}\NI know that's how you must honour him
Dialogue: 0,2:03:17.85,2:03:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但对我而言  他从来都不是那样的{\fs15}\Nbut to me, he was never that.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:20.47,2:03:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他曾{\fs15}\NHe was...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:23.01,2:03:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,对我{\fs15}\Nto me...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:26.13,2:03:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他曾{\fs15}\Nhe was...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:34.64,2:03:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我想我得快些走了{\fs15}\NWell, I think I'll slip quietly away,
Dialogue: 0,2:03:36.06,2:03:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你会帮我转告我的离别之意吧{\fs15}\Nwill you tell the others I said goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:37.65,2:03:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以自己和他们说{\fs15}\NYou can tell them yourself.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:55.89,2:03:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们再从袋底洞经过{\fs15}\NIf any of you are ever passing Bag-End...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:04.27,2:04:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,下午茶会等着你们{\fs15}\Ntea is at four.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:07.32,2:04:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那里有许多的茶{\fs15}\NThere's plenty of it...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:11.66,2:04:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,随时你的到来{\fs15}\Nand you are welcome any time.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:19.19,2:04:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哦{\fs15}\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:22.19,2:04:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不要把门敲得咚咚响就是了{\fs15}\Ndon't bother knocking.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:06.16,2:05:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 到了夏尔{\fs15}\NAhh, the borders of the...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:08.49,2:05:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,地界了{\fs15}\NShire.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:10.19,2:05:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就在这里分开吧{\fs15}\NIt is here I must leave you.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:14.78,2:05:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不好意思{\fs15}\NThat's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:18.90,2:05:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我真想有个巫师在我身旁{\fs15}\NI quite liked having a...wizard around.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:23.42,2:05:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他们真的能带来好运{\fs15}\NIt seems they bring good luck.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:25.97,2:05:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会真是那样想的 对吧{\fs15}\NYou don't really suppose, do you,
Dialogue: 0,2:05:28.23,2:05:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,所有你的冒险经历和幸免于难仅仅是因为幸运吧{\fs15}\Nthat all your adventures and escapes were managed by mere luck.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:32.35,2:05:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,魔戒不要轻易的使用了 比尔博{\fs15}\NMagic rings should not be used lightly, Bilbo.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:36.88,2:05:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不要当我是个傻子 我知道你找到了一枚 - 没有{\fs15}\NDon't take me for a fool, I know you found one... - No.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:39.80,2:05:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,在哥布林的地道里 我就一直盯着你的{\fs15}\NIn the Goblin tunnels, and I've kept my eye on you...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:43.07,2:05:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,从没离开过{\fs15}\Never since.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:47.59,2:05:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 谢天谢地{\fs15}\NWell, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:53.87,2:05:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,别了 甘道夫{\fs15}\NFarewell, Gandalf.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:58.17,2:06:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,别了{\fs15}\NFarewell.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:07.00,2:06:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你 啊{\fs15}\NYou uhh...
Dialogue: 0,2:06:08.29,2:06:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不必担心那个戒指{\fs15}\Nyou needn't worry about that ring,
Dialogue: 0,2:06:10.06,2:06:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,在战争中它从我包里掉了出来{\fs15}\Nit fell out of my pocket during the battle.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:12.18,2:06:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,找不到了{\fs15}\NI lost it.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:14.36,2:06:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你是一个非常好的人 巴金斯先生  我非常{\fs15}\NYou're a very fine person, Mr Baggins, and I'm very...
Dialogue: 0,2:06:19.62,2:06:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,欣赏你{\fs15}\Nfond of you.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:22.02,2:06:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但毕竟你也只是这广阔世界的里一个小家伙{\fs15}\NBut you're only quite a little fellow in a wide world after all.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:00.39,2:07:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 那是我母亲的荣耀盒{\fs15}\NWait a minute, that my mother's glory box.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:03.57,2:07:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那也是{\fs15}\NAnd that's...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:04.77,2:07:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我的餐椅{\fs15}\Nmy dining chair?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:06.22,2:07:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 把那给我放下{\fs15}\NHey, put that poof down!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:09.40,2:07:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事{\fs15}\NWhat is going on?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:11.32,2:07:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  比尔博先生{\fs15}\NHello, mister Bilbo.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:12.31,2:07:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你本不该在这里的{\fs15}\NYou're not supposed to be here.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:15.33,2:07:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思{\fs15}\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:17.22,2:07:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,由于假定你已经死了的缘故{\fs15}\NOn account of you being presumed dead and all.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:19.05,2:07:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我没死 假定点其它东西吧{\fs15}\NI am not dead, presumed or otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:24.56,2:07:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定那是被允许的 比尔博先生{\fs15}\NI'm not sure that's permitted. Mister Bilbo!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:28.73,2:07:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,有谁 竞拍21  21还有吗{\fs15}\N{\i1}Anyone. Any bids on 21? Any ones on 21?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:33.14,2:07:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,卖给博尔德尔{\fs15}\NSold to Mrs. Bolder!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:36.12,2:07:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,快去找个地方放你肥胖的脚吧{\fs15}\NSomewhere for Fatty to put his feet on.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:40.75,2:07:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那么这里还有一些竞价{\fs15}\NSo do I have any bids for this.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:42.00,2:07:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这是夏尔制造{\fs15}\NThis is Shire-made.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:44.59,2:07:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你们没有一件东西能和它一样 老实说{\fs15}\NNone of your Dwarvish reproductions here, honestly.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:47.28,2:07:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,停下{\fs15}\N- Stop!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:47.89,2:07:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,停下 这里有些误会{\fs15}\NStop, there's been a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:50.68,2:07:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁 - 你什么意思问我"我是谁 "{\fs15}\NWho are you? - What do you mean "who am I"?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:52.90,2:07:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定清楚的知道我是谁{\fs15}\NYou know perfectly well who I am,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:54.65,2:07:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,罗贝利亚・塞克维拉・巴金斯{\fs15}\NLobelia Sackville Baggins.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:56.72,2:07:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我家{\fs15}\NThis is my home...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:58.34,2:08:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那些是我的勺子 非常感谢{\fs15}\Nand those are my spoons, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:01.16,2:08:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这不合规矩 自从消失不见{\fs15}\NThis is most irregular. It's been more...
Dialogue: 0,2:08:03.84,2:08:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,已经过了13个月{\fs15}\Nthan 13 months since the disappearance.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:06.38,2:08:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你是真的{\fs15}\NIf you are in fact...
Dialogue: 0,2:08:08.28,2:08:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,比尔博・巴金斯 并且还没有死{\fs15}\NBilbo Baggins and undeceased?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:11.56,2:08:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你能证明吗{\fs15}\NCan you prove it?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:13.32,2:08:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,什么{\fs15}\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:14.34,2:08:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好 啊 拿些正式的{\fs15}\NWell... uh, something official...
Dialogue: 0,2:08:16.28,2:08:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,印有你名字在上面的物件就可以  - 好的{\fs15}\Nwith your name on it would suffice. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:18.86,2:08:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧{\fs15}\NRight!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:21.85,2:08:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一份雇佣合同 是作为{\fs15}\NA contract of employment as a
Dialogue: 0,2:08:24.91,2:08:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不要管那个了{\fs15}\Na but... Never mind that one.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:30.35,2:08:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这里 我的签名 - 对 好吧 哦{\fs15}\NThere, my signature. - Yes, well... uh...
Dialogue: 0,2:08:34.37,2:08:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 确实是正规手续{\fs15}\No, it certainly seems to be in order.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:36.87,2:08:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 看来不值得怀疑了{\fs15}\NYes, it seems there can be no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:39.65,2:08:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这个你把自己抵押的人是谁{\fs15}\NWho is this person you pledged your service to?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:44.16,2:08:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,索林・橡木盾{\fs15}\NThorin Oakenshield?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:49.72,2:08:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他{\fs15}\NHe...
Dialogue: 0,2:08:51.73,2:08:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我的朋友{\fs15}\Nhe was my friend.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:48.12,2:10:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不要敲了 谢谢{\fs15}\NNo, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,2:10:49.81,2:10:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不想见任何访客{\fs15}\NWe don't want any more visitors,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:52.41,2:10:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,祝福者 或者远亲{\fs15}\Nwell-wishers, or distant relations!
Dialogue: 0,2:10:54.81,2:10:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那非常老的朋友{\fs15}\NAnd what about...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:56.01,2:10:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,见不见呢{\fs15}\Nvery old friends?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:05.46,2:11:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,甘道夫 - 比尔博・巴金斯{\fs15}\NGandalf? - Bilbo Baggins!
Dialogue: 0,2:11:08.44,2:11:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我亲爱的甘道夫  - 见到你真好{\fs15}\NMy dear Gandalf! - It's good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:11.99,2:11:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,111岁了 谁会相信呢{\fs15}\NOne hundred and eleven years old. Who would believe it?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:19.75,2:11:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快来 快进来{\fs15}\NCome on, come in.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:22.03,2:11:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎 欢迎{\fs15}\NWelcome, welcome.


